"""
Attributes
payment amount(float): Indicates the payment amount for the store
payment_date (str): The date on which the payment was made
rental_unit (int): The unit number for which the payment was made
payment_status (str): Indicates if the payment is completed, pending, or overdue
Methods
set_payment_amount(float)->None: Sets the payment amount
get_payment_amount() -> float: Retrieves the payment amount
set_payment_date(date: str) -> None: Sets the date of the payment
set_rental_unit(unit: int) -> None: Sets the rental unit associated with the payment
get_rental_unit() -> int: Retrieves the rental unit number
set_payment_status(status: str) -> None: Updates the status of the payment
get_payment_status() -> str: Retrieves the status of the payment
"""
